Make the edits you want to do.

### Step 2:

When you have finished your editing. Do this:

```text
%HOMEPATH%

cd Documents\workspace\microting

git clone https://github.com/microting/eform-angular-machinearea-plugin.git
```

```text
%HOMEPATH%

cd Documents\workspace\microting
```
